            <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
            <p>The Maury mss., ca. 1935-1970, consists of the unpublished papers and writings of
                writer Curt Maury, 1909-1989. Present in this collection of mostly typescripts are
                    <title render="italic">Roadside Inns: The Final years Don Juan;</title> two
                novels; three plays, one of which was sold to Hollywood for a movie; a small group
                of poems, and eighteen short stories and novellas.</p>
        </scopecontent>

